spec_data.Name: libjson-rpc-cpp-common
spec_data.Description:
This library provides common classes for the libjson-rpc-cpp framework like:

* Exceptions
* Error-Codes
* Specification Parsers and Writers
* Procedure parameter validation

This package usually only makes sense with libjson-rpc-cpp-client and/or
libjson-rpc-cpp-server.
